{"tid":401854,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急問收炸彈人情","createTime":"2017-09-16T03:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T04:03:20.000Z","uid":135400,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3afcad5173e055ce2630e82fce236964d88b3167","tid":401854,"uid":135400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:16:00.000Z","msg":"廿幾歲人第一次做兄弟，都就黎到個日。但我地幾個兄弟之前問新郎(舊同事)有咩要準備。佢又話無。咁我地都係準備就咁恤衫西褲算，呔都唔打，新郎都話ok嘅&hellip;<br />\n點之前幾日先拉我地幾個兄弟入兄弟姊妹group，原來新娘想我地幾個兄弟全套西裝囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之後我地幾個兄弟一齊去訂西裝，都好乸利下，每人二千幾&hellip;但新郎又唔資助返我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，人地姊妹服就全包，又有利是。我地要自己去準備，重要拎二千幾自費買西裝。又要做咕喱擔擔抬抬&hellip;<br />\n問：咁佢地中午擺酒，唔係夜晚。身為兄弟要比幾多人情？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：舊同事新郎唔算太熟，兩三年先見返一兩次。覺得做兄弟好搵笨&hellip;<br />\n希望有經驗嘅巴打絲打幫手解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0cf296a1cf8d5ba75643e411f81d2bcc3bb3a5e","tid":401854,"uid":135400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e200805a96ee899243656ade1dd463a2fb665d","tid":401854,"uid":81982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"蘋果日報"},{"pid":"4dc6b8c39c7f8865da3791ac62d99cfb9cb22b3c","tid":401854,"uid":5112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:57:19.000Z","msg":"兄弟都要比？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8128e65f9151df68c9287ce99b33702fbcc2b98","tid":401854,"uid":14753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"兄弟好似唔使比 有心咪送份祝物"},{"pid":"8742362d7b427c4b2b52767af7562596edca31fd","tid":401854,"uid":14753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:58:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兄弟好似唔使比 有心咪送份禮物</blockquote>"},{"pid":"cb69983b3d1ac74ea0a8036cc65f80513987f5b5","tid":401854,"uid":1646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T03:59:27.000Z","msg":"唔熟做乜鳩兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cd197fbec98e0fa6efe0e1d3542817a3666e32","tid":401854,"uid":7961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:00:24.000Z","msg":"唔熟就應該唔做兄弟<br />\n同埋多數係新郎俾埋...<br />\n如果食午餐，咪俾500-800囉...<br />\n但你咁既情況..睇下其他巴打教你路啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73c51576191194e0146d0b8ee019255f16a991c","tid":401854,"uid":105445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:03:20.000Z","msg":"西裝錢都要自己俾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我以前做新郎家乜都包曬仲封返封利士俾我地呀 大佬 幫佢做左咁多日咕喱唔通仲要自己出錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇撚野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}